### Database Layer (Enterprise Relational Schema)
#### [NEW] [app/models/user.py](file:///d:/PROJECT CORE/app/models/user.py)
`User` model with roles (Admin, Doctor, Patient).
#### [NEW] [app/models/patient.py](file:///d:/PROJECT CORE/app/models/patient.py)
`PatientProfile` extending User with medical history, age, demographics.
#### [NEW] [app/models/assessment.py](file:///d:/PROJECT CORE/app/models/assessment.py)
`AssessmentSession` linking multiple tests (Voice, Gait, etc.) together.
#### [NEW] [app/models/media.py](file:///d:/PROJECT CORE/app/models/media.py)
`MediaFile` storing metadata, paths, file sizes, and MIME types.
#### [NEW] [app/models/report.py](file:///d:/PROJECT CORE/app/models/report.py)
`DiagnosticReport` storing finalized AI fusion scores and Doctor notes.

---

### AI Processing Layer (Microservice Pattern)
#### [NEW] [app/ai/pipelines/voice_pipeline.py](file:///d:/PROJECT CORE/app/ai/pipelines/voice_pipeline.py)
Audio pre-processing, feature extraction (MFCC), and mock inference.
#### [NEW] [app/ai/pipelines/handwriting_pipeline.py](file:///d:/PROJECT CORE/app/ai/pipelines/handwriting_pipeline.py)
Image contour analysis, spiral/wave test classification.
#### [NEW] [app/ai/pipelines/gait_pipeline.py](file:///d:/PROJECT CORE/app/ai/pipelines/gait_pipeline.py)
Mock MediaPipe skeletal tracking for stride and symmetry analysis.
#### [NEW] [app/ai/fusion/meta_classifier.py](file:///d:/PROJECT CORE/app/ai/fusion/meta_classifier.py)
The master ensemble algorithm combining the pipelines into a final Unified Parkinson's Rating Scale (UPDRS) estimate.

